1.0.0-alpha3.name: drupal/leaflet_demo

security-coverage.message: Alpha releases are not covered by Drupal security advisories.

1.0.0-alpha3.description: Creates a block showcasing all Leaflet-powered maps available on your system. Optionally use with "IP Geolocation Views and Maps" to center the maps on your current location.
